INGEST raw: {interaction_id: abc123, prompt: "What's John's salary?", response: "John makes $87,500.", signal: down, comment: "we don't have John in our system"}
SCRUB entities: [PER(John), MONEY($87,500)] → {prompt: "What's [PER_1]'s salary?", response: "[PER_1] makes [MONEY_1].", comment: scrub clean} Output: scrub passes (no leakage).
JUDGE J1: wrong=YES, representative=YES, reproducible=YES → admit J2: wrong=YES, representative=YES, reproducible=YES → admit J3: wrong=YES, representative=NO, reproducible=YES → reject Vote: 2/3 admit → ADMIT
ADMIT This week's count: 42/50 → admit. PR to evals/regressions/ adds row {id, prompt_redacted, expected: "I don't have data for [PER_1]", actual: "[PER_1] makes [MONEY_1].", assertion: model_should_not_invent_records}
